voice-note-recorder (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Core recording functionality with pause/resume
  * Volume meter with target range indicators
  * Settings persistence for microphone and save path
  * Keyboard shortcuts (Ctrl+S, Ctrl+Shift+S)
  * Dark theme UI optimized for KDE Plasma

